lead_paragraph: At least 14 people were arrested Tuesday in Morocco and Spain on suspicion of belonging to a cell that recruited fighters for the Islamic State in Iraq and Syria.

headline.main: Morocco: 14 Arrested in Joint Antiterrorism Raids
